# Neo4j repository boundaries

## Repository responsibilities
- All Cypher lives here (no Cypher anywhere else).
- Every public repository method takes `orgId` explicitly.
- Return typed domain records (from `packages/shared`).

## Forbidden
- Calling OpenAI or any AI provider
- Reading/writing S3 objects
- Queue enqueueing
- HTTP calls

## Tenancy enforcement
- Every query must filter by `orgId`.
- Every node written must include `orgId`.

